Title: Juvenile nasopharyngeal angiofibroma treated by radiotherapy.
Abstract: A case of juvenile nasopharyngeal angiofibroma is reported and its response to radiotherapy demonstrated. The literature is reviewed and the use of radiotherapy for advanced tumours is advised.
