Title: Pseudomyxoma peritonei treated by radiotherapy.
Abstract: Pseudomyxoma peritonei (PP) is a rare condition. Treatment is usually unsuccessful and the prognosis is poor. This report describes a patient who survived 16 years following their initial presentation.
