Title: Cancer of the adrenal cortex treated by O,P"-DDD (author's transl).
Abstract: Presentation of a case of cancer of the adrenal cortex with hypercorticism, treated by surgery and o,p'-DDD, with temporary clinical and biological remission. The indications and results of chemotherapy with o,p'-DDD are discussed.
